file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
# Added by API Auto Mocking Plugin
servers:
  - description: SwaggerHub API Auto Mocking
    url: https://virtserver.swaggerhub.com/danhunsaker/hoarder-warehouse/1.0.0
  - description: Individual application server
    url: https://{host}:7410
    variables:
      host:
        default: ''
        description: The host IP of the server
info:
  version: '1.0.0'
  title: 'Hoarder Data Warehouse API'
  description: 'The API spec for the Hoarder data warehouse component.'
paths:
  /ping:
    get:
      summary: Check Hoarder status
      security: []
      responses:
        200:
          description: ''
          content:
            text/plain:
              example: |
                pong
  /blobs:
    get:
      summary: List all blobs
      tags: [blobs]
      responses:
        200:
          description: ''
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  type: object
                  properties:
                    Name:
                      type: string
                    Size:
                      type: integer
                    ModTime:
                      type: string
              example:
                - Name: app-Al4eXxxs183nGacj8ITfhaNJn235pM.tgz
                  Size: 490020874
                  ModTime: '2020-01-17T04:43:58.319309789Z'
  /blobs/{name}:
    parameters:
      - name: name
        in: path
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
    get:
      summary: Retrieve a blob
      tags: [blobs]
      responses:
        200:
          description: ''
          content:
            text/plain:
              example: test
    post:
      summary: Publish a new blob
      tags: [blobs]
      requestBody:
        content:
          text/plain:
            schema:
              type: string
            example: data
      responses:
        200:
          description: ''
          content:
            text/plain:
              example: "'test' created!"
    put:
      summary: Update an existing blob
      tags: [blobs]
      requestBody:
        content:
          text/plain:
            schema:
              type: string
            example: data
      responses:
        200:
          description: ''
          content:
            text/plain:
              example: "'test' created!"
    delete:
      summary: Remove an existing blob
      tags: [blobs]
      responses:
        200:
          description: ''
          content:
            text/plain:
              example: "'test' destroyed!"
components:
  securitySchemes:
    Token:
      type: apiKey
      name: X-Auth-Token
      in: header
security:
 - Token: []
